description.text:
I used <a rel="nofollow" href="http://dkprojects.net/openscad-threads/" >Dan Kirshner's OpenSCAD threads library</a>, with the following settings:
<code >detergent_cap_outer_diameter = 34.3;
detergent_cap_inner_diameter = 32.9;
//Height of the cap.
detergent_cap_height = 11.4;
//Interior depth inside the cap. Same axis as height.
detergent_cap_depth = 10;

detergent_cap_thread_pitch = 5;

metric_thread(internal=true, groove=true, thread_size=1, square=false, pitch=detergent_cap_thread_pitch, diameter=detergent_cap_inner_diameter, length=detergent_cap_depth);</code>
